ls=\"aria-mchl97209c0d\" class=\"Name\">Expand or collapse a desktop stack</h2><div class=\"TaskBody\" role=\"region\" aria-hidden=\"false\" id=\"aria-mchl97209c0d\"><p>On your Mac, do any of the following:</p><ul><li><p><em>Expand a stack: </em>Click it on the desktop. When the stack’s expanded, double-click any item to open it.</p></li><li><p><em>Collapse a stack: </em>Click its Down Arrow icon.</p></li></ul></div></div><div id=\"mchl6b7b6ff1\" class=\"Task\"><h2 aria-controls=\"aria-mchl6b7b6ff1\" class=\"Name\">Change how desktop stacks are grouped</h2><div class=\"TaskBody\" role=\"region\" aria-hidden=\"false\" id=\"aria-mchl6b7b6ff1\"><p>You can group stacks by kind (such as images or PDFs), date (such as the date a file was last opened or created), or Finder tags.</p><ul><li><p>On your Mac, click the desktop, choose View &gt; Group Stacks By, then choose an option. Or Control-click the desktop, choose Group Stacks By, then choose an option.</p></li></ul></div></div><div id=\"mchl273f7d0d\" class=\"Task\"><h2 aria-controls=\"aria-mchl273f7d0d\" class=\"Name\">Change the appearance of desktop stacks</h2><div class=\"TaskBody\" role=\"region\" aria-hidden=\"false\" id=\"aria-mchl273f7d0d\"><p>You can make icons bigger, change the spacing between icons, move icon labels to the side, or show more information (such as how many files are in a stack).</p><ul><li><p>On your Mac, click the desktop, choose View &gt; Show View Options, then change options. Or Control-click the desktop, choose Show View Options, then change options.</p></li></ul></div></div><p>You can display folders in the Dock as stacks. See <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=use-folders-in-the-dock&amp;version=13.0&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MCHL231F08FB&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=13.0\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">Use folders in the Dock</a>.</p><div class=\"LinkUniversal\"><strong>See also</strong><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=work-on-the-desktop&amp;version=13.0&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MH40612&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=13.0\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">Get to know the Mac desktop</a></div></body>","tags":[{"type":"audience","refKey":"PUBLIC_USERS","tagPath":"audience/PUBLIC_USERS","title":"Public"}]}]},"categoryInfo":{"categories":["IP-Meta/DesignVersion/DesignVersion2","platform/mac","DisplayVersion/macOS Ventura 13","MetaFollow/MetaFollowOFF","ContentMode/liveContent","SupportSearchIndex/SupportSearchIndexON","ArchivalStatus/Archived","ExternalIndex/ExternalIndexOFF"],"categoryDictionaries":[{"key":"SupportSearchIndexON","name":"SupportSearchIndexON","englishName":"SupportSearchIndexON","displayName":"SupportSearchIndexON","articleCount":"120736"},{"key":"liveContent","name":"Live Content","englishName":"Live Content","displayName":"Live Content","articleCount":"135880"},{"key":"IP-Meta","name":"IP-Meta","englishName":"IP-Meta","displayName":"IP-Meta","articleCount":"0"},{"key":"ContentMode","name":"ContentMode","englishName":"ContentMode","displayName":"ContentMode","articleCount":"0"},{"key":"DesignVersion2","name":"DesignVersion 2","englishName":"DesignVersion 2","displayName":"DesignVersion 2","articleCount":"135315"},{"key":"MetaFollow","name":"MetaFollow","englishName":"MetaFollow","displayName":"MetaFollow","articleCount":"0"},{"key":"ExternalIndex","name":"ExternalIndex","englishName":"ExternalIndex","displayName":"ExternalIndex","articleCount":"0"},{"key":"DesignVersion","name":"DesignVersion","englishName":"DesignVersion","displayName":"DesignVersion","articleCount":"0"},{"key":"mac","name":"mac","englishName":"mac","displayName":"mac","articleCount":"85819"},{"key":"platform","name":"platform","englishName":"platform","displayName":"platform","articleCount":"0"},{"key":"Archived","name":"Archived","englishName":"Archived","displayName":"Archived","articleCount":"124678"},{"key":"ArchivalStatus","name":"Archiv